mods.abstract: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Wynonna at the Grand Ole Opry House on February 1 in order to film Her Story: Scenes from a Lifetime. Event proceeds benefit the W.O. Smith Community Music School. Poster features a metal photoplate of Wynonna Judd.
